reviews.text: The taste of the food was fine. However the chef was careless to say the least. Seafood was served with the shell unopened. After an order was taken, menu was left on the table. Water refilling wasn't done until reminded. That said, the attitude was okay. Water refilling was non-stopped after the first complaint. The waitresses were very eager to collect the used plate. $240 for two dinner on a Saturday night.
The movenpick ice cream is really lovely (cost is $75 for 3 scoops) but the dessert in the picture was just okay. That was about sixty something dollars.
Good food. Not pricey. Don't need to wait for a very long time. The place is comfortable. People are nice. I will recommend this place for a little friend gethering.
Great food👍
I had the All Day Breakfast, it was good.  Butter for the toast would have been better.  The kitchen was slow to make my meal, but took and delivered my order efficiently.

result.name: Say Cheese

reviews.text:
1. 薯條炸得ok，少油，但太少醬
2. 海鮮焗飯係災難，仲衰過茶記，得一隻蝦同3隻蜆3隻青口仔，飯完全冇香味
3. 黑松露手搓粉：味道可以，但過百蚊一碟，份量少得可憐
（聽到隔離枱投訴豬肋骨肉太韌）
4. 冇主動斟水，成日要叫，叫完又唔記得，人手不足
Short comment: Mediocre food quality and service

The taste of the food was fine. However the chef was careless to say the least. Seafood was served with the shell unopened. After an order was taken, menu was left on the table. Water refilling wasn't done until reminded. That said, the attitude was okay. Water refilling was non-stopped after the first complaint. The waitresses were very eager to collect the used plate. $240 for two dinner on a Saturday night.
食物選擇少，份量更少，味道一般。
价格合適，午餐食物可以。甜品比較貴。座位舒適。員工人手不足。
食物味道質數都中上，座位整潔，氣氛悠閒，唯獨下午茶餐份量偏少，咖啡選擇種類比較少!其他都滿意!
